dc_title_s: South Trenton Proposed Exterior Pier and Solid Filling Lines
dc_description_s: Map 1: Map covers area from Delaware River to Union Street. Map shows proposed pierhead line and proposed exterior line for solid filling between Bridge and Ferry Streets. There is a recept attached to the map, addressed to John C. Payne from the Pennsylvania Railroad Company.|Map 2: Map covers area from Grove Street to Ferry Street. There is a recept attached to the map, addressed to John C. Payne from the Pennsylvania Railroad Company.
